SOLDIER 

SKILL PROFICIENCIES: Athletics, Intimidation
TOOL PROFICIENCIES: One type of a gaming set, Vehicles (land)
EQUIPMENT: Insignia of rank
           Trophy of fallen enemy
           Set of bone dice || deck of cards
           Set of common clothes 
           Belt pouch containing 10gp
           
SPECIALTY 
(d8)

FEATURE: MILITARY RANK
Other soldiers still recognize rank. 
Use rank to influence other soldiers (simple equipment || horses) temporarily 
Access to friendly camps

